{"tid":1081834,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片睇】Samsung 公開 Galaxy Fold 耐用測試片段　機器不斷對摺手機","createTime":"2019-03-28T13:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T07:36:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c769b744a8c354fbaf144d1a6c6d0df67b20f60d","tid":1081834,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/McdgS3Popjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMcdgS3Popjk&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7APno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=6155137d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/McdgS3Popjk</a><br />\n<br />\nSamsung 早於今年 2 月，發布旗下首部熒幕摺疊手機 Galaxy Fold ，讓不少支持者感到十分驚奇。雖然 Samsung 方面早已表示，新機的 Infinity Flex 熒幕及鉸鏈經過一系列測試，證實可以經得起 20 萬次摺疊。不過，外界亦十分關注手機熒幕的耐用程度。如今， Samsung 更於網上公開他們的實際測試過程，釋除外界疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上，早前 YouTube 上曾有試玩片段流出，當中可見 Galaxy Fold 的摺痕相當明顯，引起外界憂慮產品的耐用程度。外媒《Engadget》指出，從最近公開的官方測試片段中，仍然可以看到 Galaxy Fold 上的摺痕，但在影片某些鏡頭則看不到摺痕的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外媒《Engadget》亦指當 Galaxy Fold 摺起時，熒幕對摺的角度只有 85 度，並非完全對摺。因此當用家將摺起的 Galaxy Fold 放在桌面上時，熒幕亦不會完全平放。相信對要求較高的用家來說，仍要留待真機登場才能夠好好檢查清楚了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Engadget<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7APno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=5a2cc9da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7APno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=cc22dcc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7APno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=bfb1e53d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/28/samsung-galaxy-fold-duration-test/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F28%2Fsamsung-galaxy-fold-duration-test%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7APno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=ae7e0c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/28/samsung-galaxy-fold-duration-test/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"045e461ad595c77f775029f66a43fdc4bc8e87f4","tid":1081834,"uid":1130,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"屎為果部呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f8eb8de460c893656d5f03734d0bf662fdc6d5","tid":1081834,"uid":34213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"045e461ad595c77f775029f66a43fdc4bc8e87f4","tid":1081834,"uid":1130,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"屎為果部呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"要再挖角先偷到部對摺機"},{"pid":"51815da3e86753765073ee26b272fab852ea350e","tid":1081834,"uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"對摺個較位耐用又點姐...重點係痴唔到mon貼+膠面mon 求其有條鎖匙銀一銀都花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d042911754f2c3e7950028a0ed8b9f56ac6416","tid":1081834,"uid":191352,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca930f575e5d648da6a88c4eab3a598d1f55e33d","tid":1081834,"uid":12412,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"撚頭咁大，吹到咁大點收科"},{"pid":"04382de0c2e82eca55ff9b3a8844d22e8fccbbf6","tid":1081834,"uid":90259,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"51815da3e86753765073ee26b272fab852ea350e","tid":1081834,"uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"對摺個較位耐用又點姐...重點係痴唔到mon貼+膠面mon 求其有條